      "rationale": "The Power Law hemolysis model (Giersiepen et al. coefficients) was selected based on its established use in FDA-cited hemolysis prediction literature. The k-omega SST turbulence model was selected for its validated performance in confined rotating flow applications. Model form uncertainty quantification beyond this justification is not required at MRL 2."
