    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels at MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per the ASME V&V 40 framework. Validation results demonstrate that CFD-predicted hemolysis index values satisfy the RH < 1 acceptance criterion across all five COU operating points, with quantitative comparison metrics within acceptable bounds. The model is judged credible for its intended use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
